title: Importing tensorflow after import pytorch crashes inside tensorflow::port::TestCPUFeature
body_html:
TF version: 07bf1d3
PyTorch version: '0.2.0_4' (whatever is installed by default yesterday)

Crashing code

import torch
import tensorflow

Work-around

import torch
